直企係示威者呢邊，亦都係撐天琦。被爆眼女手足單野佢都有出片做證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/567628880005099/posts/1955710974530209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F567628880005099%2Fposts%2F1955710974530209%2F&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU%2F2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=d38b05d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/567628880005099/posts/1955710974530209/</a><br />\n佢出左篇Facebook Post講今晚既感受。<br />\n護公安嘅鬼佬記者出咗聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467248</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"你條片左cut 右cut"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:17:26.000Z","msg":"睇佢自己出既facebook post"},{"pid":"2a4f22c1e819ecee21e02797f3652bdb1d94a16b","tid":1468152,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"不割席 不分化 兄弟爬山<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">弱點已經比敵人對準！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要搵幾條仆街帶風就已經成功破解我哋呢三句格言！！<br />\n<br />\n不割不分吖嘛！！<br />\n搵人帶風自然有人跟！！<br />\n搵鬼落場做乜嘢都可以入你數！<br />\n<br />\n再唔諗辦法<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">捉鬼</span></strong>，我哋真係死撚硬！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">兄弟不割，鬼同分化撚一定要割</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要有效捉鬼，前線一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有底線共識</span></strong>，咩可以做，咩唔可以做，一過底線就係鬼，即捉！唔係割席，唔係分化呀！係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">認真解決問題呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分化同鬼從來都係狗共致勝之道<br />\n，要對付唯一方法就係<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">團結</span></strong></strong>！！<br />\n既然團結，就嘗試傾個底線共識，唔係所有野要有共識，底線真係有須要呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定捉鬼呀！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">底線共識大家可以討論</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大前提係畀全世界知我哋係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">為自由良知而戰嘅正義之師，係保護市民嘅黑衣人！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.可以打遊擊同快閃， 唔放火/唔掉磚/唔衝/唔主動出手/唔傷及無無辜。<br />\n<br />\n2. 可以佔路set路障，圍，口撩，還拖！但不主動出擊，不傷及無辜。<br />\n<br />\n3.不送頭，所有可以被聯上暴動同暴徒嘅，都唔好做。<br />\n<br />\n4. 贏輿論同民心唔係講緊連登呀！自high有乜撚嘢用！<br />\n<br />\n輿論係正常媒體包括 social media 同埋國際輿論，民心唔使講啦！<br />\n<br />\n失民心同輿論，話撚知你連登幾high幾高漲，大家可以返屋企含撚啦！<br />\n<br />\n輿論同民心係要嚟令對家喺國際/同社會有壓力！<br />\n<br />\n只要set到個底線嘅共識， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋先可以真正團結，<strong><strong></strong></strong>先有機會贏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁我先真正做到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山 不割席 不分化！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足認真諗諗啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b423043a30563c498f590925119027f0a7f92e4","tid":1468152,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9cc5f72dd5f49ee2eca18cf304d64c4ecb717e8","tid":1468152,"uid":298428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:19:55.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非 取消黑衫行動 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透</span>"},{"pid":"59c8c19e980cca021a47f954a03c889e1dfb5d85","tid":1468152,"uid":136303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:51.000Z","msg":"之後應該咁樣玩<br />\n重推 每日癱瘓機場8小時<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467885</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cac49bb7bb074d15c856592b10b369668856e177","tid":1468152,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}